00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,600
Here's what science actually says about natural killer cells.

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:06,000
They're not your regular immune cells.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:09,200
These warriors patrol your body, ready to attack.

4
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:14,400
Natural killer cells recognize and destroy infected or cancerous cells without prior exposure.

5
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:20,800
Recent studies suggest they play a vital role in immunotherapy, helping us fight cancer more effectively.

6
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:27,200
But, preliminary research shows we still have much to learn about how to enhance their power.

